sk is dropped. The `act` should manually check for cancellation via `IO.checkCanceled` if it wants to react\n  to that. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L117-L118","name":"BaseIO.mapTask","link":"./../semantic/17257034048184449093.xml#","docLink":"./Init/System/IO.html#BaseIO.mapTask","doc":"See `BaseIO.asTask`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L122-L123","name":"BaseIO.bindTask","link":"./../semantic/11982490333761907337.xml#","docLink":"./Init/System/IO.html#BaseIO.bindTask","doc":"See `BaseIO.asTask`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L125-L131","name":"BaseIO.mapTasks","link":"./../semantic/9624263982319553109.xml#","docLink":"./Init/System/IO.html#BaseIO.mapTasks","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L128-L131","name":"BaseIO.mapTasks.go","link":"./../semantic/15841804138086935943.xml#","docLink":"./Init/System/IO.html#BaseIO.mapTasks.go","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L138-L139","name":"EIO.asTask","link":"./../semantic/14819062376051101579.xml#","docLink":"./Init/System/IO.html#EIO.asTask","doc":"`EIO` specialization of `BaseIO.asTask`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L142-L143","name":"EIO.mapTask","link":"./../semantic/4394760030920261143.xml#","docLink":"./Init/System/IO.html#EIO.mapTask","doc":"`EIO` specialization of `BaseIO.mapTask`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/System/IO.lean#L146-L147","name":"EIO.bindTask","link":"./../seman