,"docLink":"./Init/Data/Option/Basic.html#Option.all","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/Data/Option/Basic.lean#L60-L62","name":"Option.any","link":"./../semantic/11601258715448450791.xml#","docLink":"./Init/Data/Option/Basic.html#Option.any","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/Data/Option/Basic.lean#L64-L66","name":"Option.orElse","link":"./../semantic/2883509574793695409.xml#","docLink":"./Init/Data/Option/Basic.html#Option.orElse","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/Data/Option/Basic.lean#L68-L69","name":"Option.instOrElseOption","link":"./../semantic/1488383565827767855.xml#","docLink":"./Init/Data/Option/Basic.html#Option.instOrElseOption","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/Data/Option/Basic.lean#L71-L74","name":"Option.lt","link":"./../semantic/12991490994501194223.xml#","docLink":"./Init/Data/Option/Basic.html#Option.lt","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/Data/Option/Basic.lean#L76-L80","name":"Option.instDecidableRelOptionLt","link":"./../semantic/13338405661943211819.xml#","docLink":"./Init/Data/Option/Basic.html#Option.instDecidableRelOptionLt","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/Data/Option/Basic.lean#L84-L84","name":"instDecidableEqOption","link":"./../semantic/8131932504217798495.xml#","docLink":"./Init/Data/Option/Basic.html#instDecidableEqOption","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/56cd6c1ff519d8be39f35875b5bf8719e6101c20/src/Init/Data/Option/Basic.lean#L85-L85","name":"instBEqOption","link":"./../semantic/11588110535516121057.xml#","docLink":"./In